# Normalize text files to LF in the repo. Working-tree checkouts use the
# platform's native line ending, but anything committed is LF — keeps
# diffs clean across macOS / Linux / Windows contributors.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Treat known binary types explicitly so git doesn't try to text-normalize
# them on checkout.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.webp binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.mp4 binary
*.zip binary
